 encapsulation source-address 2001:DB8:3::3
 locator PE2 ipv6-prefix 2001:DB8:130:: 64 static 32
 opcode ::200 end-dt4 vpn-instance vpn1 evpn
#
isis 1
 is-level level-1
 cost-style wide
 network-entity 10.0000.0000.0003.00
 #
